{"TopicId":178162,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"New KSP fan theory!","CreatedByName":"TheEndHathCome","CreatedById":190848,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T05:20:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheEndHathCome","CreatedById":190848,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T05:20:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had an idea on why the kerbals living/working at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E appear to be the only living creatures on Kerbin, as well as why they are so totally focused on space exploration.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThe Monoliths:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy theory is that the Kerbol system is in the same universe as the aliens (who created the Monoliths) in 2001: a space odyssey. There are numerous monoliths dotted around the Kerbol system, with no apparent explanation for their presence.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDisappointed by the progress of the human race (who were more focused on fighting then exploring) the aliens sent Monoliths to another star, in an attempt to create and cultivate another space faring species. They created kerbals from the primordial soup, making sure there were only a few hundred to prevent significant tribal wars/conflicts. The aliens left the monoliths on Kerbin and around Kerbol to monitor the kerbals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe reason the kerbals are so obsessed with going into space is because the aliens/monoliths have programmed this into them since they were born. The aliens chose the Kerbol system for the life because the lower gravity and smaller celestial bodies made it easier for the kerbals to build rockets and explore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-09-09T05:21:35Z\u0022 title=\u002209/09/2018 05:21  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by TheEndHathCome\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T05:23:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis work of a fan has been moved to Fan Works. And welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T06:33:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI liek this.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T13:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EOooo, noice theory!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-10T17:23:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo why are the only kerbals at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-10T18:30:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223448779\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536600180\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kernel Kraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kernel Kraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo why are the only kerbals at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause that is the only important place on Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEndHathCome","CreatedById":190848,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-11T07:46:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223448779\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536600180\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kernel Kraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Kernel Kraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo why are the only kerbals at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCause as Cubinator said, this is the most important\u00A0place on Kerbin. The \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E (being Kerbin\u0027s space port) is where the entire Kerbal civilisation is focused, because of the central role it plays in their society.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-12T00:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI too like this.\u00A0 However correction: gravity is the same as Earth or the Moon.\u00A0 Maybe they chose the Kerbol system due to its economical size \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Minmus Derp","CreatedById":187595,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-16T23:50:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EDis is a good theory. BUT. How are kerbals almost immortal?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EAnd also, why are every generation\u0027s veteran kerbals named Jeb, Bill, Bob and Val?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEndHathCome","CreatedById":190848,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-17T07:49:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223452396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221537141854\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187595\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Minmus Derp\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, The Minmus Derp said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EDis is a good theory. BUT. How are kerbals almost immortal?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EAnd also, why are every generation\u0027s veteran kerbals named Jeb, Bill, Bob and Val?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell, to answer one of your queries, I think that the aliens intervene slightly with life on kerbin by making its in inhabitants immortal, thus, time isn\u0027t wasted teaching new generations how to build and design spacecraft.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Minmus Derp","CreatedById":187595,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-17T11:34:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223452560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221537170583\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022190848\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheEndHathCome\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, TheEndHathCome said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell, to answer one of your queries, I think that the aliens intervene slightly with life on kerbin by making its in inhabitants immortal, thus, time isn\u0027t wasted teaching new generations how to build and design spacecraft.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EOh i see.\u00A0 But also,\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223452396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221537141854\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187595\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Minmus Derp\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, The Minmus Derp said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sa